title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 316: Featuring Brady Tkachuk & Nathan MacKinnon
description:
On Episode 316, the guys are joined by Brady Tkachuk and Nathan MacKinnon. Brady joined (1:00:07) to discuss the pesky Sens, Jimmy Stu, the North Division and tons more. The guys also break down the full start of the NHL season, division by division, and cover all the NHL news including the Keith Yandle saga in Florida. The fellas are then joined by Nate Dogg (1:57:01) who discussed the Avs, the Sandbagger, acting in Trailer Park Boys and a bunch more. The boys wrap up talking some NFL, Mark Messier turning 60 years old and RA does a Gambling Corner (02:53:02).


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
